***************************************
* You might run into troubles running *
* tcpdump, you should recompile it if *
* it segfaults:                       *
* $ cd /usr/src/usr.sbin/tcpdump      *
* $ make && make install              *
***************************************
* You can always reinstall the older  *
* libraries via the source directory  *
* of the base system:                 *
* $ cd /usr/src/lib/libpcap           *
* $ make && make install              *
***************************************
